data.description: Charming home in Monte Viejo with a great open floor plan. Home features an eat-in kitchen with a smooth cooktop, tons of storage, custom paint, and spacious bedrooms with walk-in closets. Spacious backyard with privacy fence and a patio slab perfect for gatherings. New roof, new HVAC, solar panels(owned). Great location; close to downtown, restaurants, and shopping. Schedule your showing today and make this your home!
